WEBVTT

00:08:27.570 --> 00:08:30.490
beyond our limits.

00:08:30.490 --> 00:08:33.860
And although today is about
innovation without borders,

00:08:33.860 --> 00:08:37.000
I have to say that in my life,

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:39.428
innovation has only been possible

00:08:39.428 --> 00:08:42.600
because of my borders.

00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:47.005
I've learned that borders are where the actual ends,

00:08:47.005 --> 00:08:50.000
but also where the imagination

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:52.930
and the story begins.

00:08:52.930 --> 00:08:55.916
So the thought that I would like 
to challenge you with today

00:08:55.916 --> 00:08:59.994
is that maybe instead of looking at 
our challenges and our limitations

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:03.000
as something negative or bad,